<div class="section-container">
                <h2 class="faq-title hero__overlay-title section-title has-animated">
                    Shoes Authentication FAQs
                </h2>
            <div class="new-faq_wrapp">
                <div class="new-faq_item">
                    <div class="new-faq_item-title">
                        <p class="font-title">
                            Can I legit check sneakers?
                        </p>
                        <a href="javascript:void(0)"  class="font-title">
                            +
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="new-faq_item-text">
                        <p class="font-description">
                           Certainly, our team specializes in authenticating a wide range of luxury products, including sneakers authentication. If you have purchased sneakers from any of the brands listed on our website (you can find them <a href="https://legitgrails.com/pages/choose-your-brand">here</a>), we can provide authentication services for them.
<br><br>
All you need to do is send us high-quality pictures of your footwear, ensuring good lighting to capture the details effectively. Additionally, select the desired authentication timeframe that suits your needs.
<br><br>
Once our experts have completed the authentication process, you will receive a confirmation of the sneakers' authenticity, along with a certificate. 
<br><br>
This certificate not only enhances the selling value of your item but also provides reassurance about the legitimacy of your sneakers. That's all there is to it! 
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="new-faq_item">
                    <div class="new-faq_item-title">
                        <p class="font-title">
                            How do you check if the shoes are legit?
                        </p>
                        <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="font-title">
                            +
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="new-faq_item-text">
                        <p class="font-description">
                           We have a diverse team of experts who specialize in various brands and product categories. It's important to note that a pair of shoes will not be authenticated by a jewelry expert, and vice versa.
<br><br>
Each product from a specific brand possesses unique characteristics that set it apart from counterfeits. These distinct traits are precisely what we examine when determining the authenticity of a product.
<br><br>
If you are interested in learning more about how to authenticate specific brands or products, we invite you to explore our comprehensive guides available here. These guides provide detailed information on the methods to verify the authenticity of various products.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="new-faq_item">
                    <div class="new-faq_item-title">
                        <p class="font-title">
                          What happens if you buy counterfeit shoes?
                        </p>
                        <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="font-title">
                            +
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="new-faq_item-text">
                        <p class="font-description">
                            Buying counterfeit shoes can have several negative consequences. Firstly, counterfeit shoes are typical of inferior quality and durability, leading to discomfort and potential foot damage.
<br><br>
Moreover, fake shoes lack the authenticity and craftsmanship that are characteristic of genuine products. This diminishes their overall value and desirability. It's worth noting that wearing counterfeit shoes in jurisdictions where counterfeit goods are strictly regulated can even result in legal consequences.
<br><br>
That's why it's always advisable to verify the authenticity of a product, especially if it was not purchased directly from an authorized retailer such as a Gucci store. Consulting an expert can help you identify and eliminate fake products, potentially enabling you to seek a refund for any damages incurred along the way.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
            </div>
  <div class="new-faq_bottom font-title">
      <p>Have more questions? Visit our <a href="https://legitgrails.frontkb.com/en">Help Center</a></p>
  </div>
